Steps to run the code:

1. clone the repo.
2. on base path, run "npm i" //it will install all required package
3. RUN the command "npm run dev". It will start server on port 3000
4. open browser and run "localhost:3000"
5. Open in mutiple tabs the same url "localhost:3000"
6. if you type in one tab, other will disabled and will be enabled if it is out of focus.


Tech stack used:
NodeJs, Express, Socket.io
We are serving index.html via our node server.